            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Cory! I brought the milk!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, it's true... Sophie, you're such a kind and caring person..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x27,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You've done so much for me, please let me thank you by working for you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "A-ahaha... You don't have to act anymore, Cory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Grr, you knew?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes. You asked me to get you some milk so I didn't have to worry about you working for free."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, I actually really did want to drink some milk..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Huh, really!? It was all true!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, moving on... I'll do the work you asked for now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Cory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's just that I'll need a little time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It seems to be a pretty complicated item... If I rush it, I could..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right. The \"toll\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'm very sorry, but I think it'll take about a week. Is that still okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, of course. I'm just thankful that you'll do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "There's no rush. Take your time, and don't push yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "...I understand. I'll take my time, but try to finish it as quickly as I can."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Okay, thanks!"
        }
    ]
}